* Current GPIB command character being processed
label 004A current_gpib_cmd

* SRQ pending flag (0x55 = SRQ needs servicing, 0x00 = idle)
label 004B srq_pending

* GPIB line terminator flag (0x7F=CR/LF seen, 0xFF=with error)
